name: Baccarat Rouge 540 Eau de Parfum
description: An iconic signature scent, luminous and sophisticated, born from the encounter between Maison Francis Kurkdjian and Baccarat.

name: Baccarat Rouge 540 Extrait de Parfum
description: A more concentrated and intense version of Baccarat Rouge 540, amplifying its amber and woody facets.

name: Oud Mood
description: A deep and captivating oriental oud fragrance, part of the Oud Mood collection.

name: Oud Silk Mood
description: A soft and airy oud fragrance, like silk caressing the skin, with rose and chamomile notes.

name: Oud Satin Mood
description: A rich and elegant fragrance that weaves together oud from Laos, rose absolute from Turkey, and vanilla.

name: Oud Cashmere Mood
description: A warm and enveloping oud fragrance, like a soft cashmere wrap, with notes of labdanum and vanilla.

name: Oud Velvet Mood
description: A rich and luxurious oud fragrance, deep and velvety, with cinnamon and saffron.

name: Aqua Universalis Cologne Forte
description: A radiant fresh scent, a joyful explosion of white musk and bergamot.

name: Aqua Universalis Forte
description: A more intense and lasting version of Aqua Universalis, amplifying its clean and fresh character.

name: Aqua Vitae Cologne Forte
description: A sunny and vibrant fresh scent, a whirlwind of fresh citrus and floral notes.

name: Aqua Vitae Forte
description: A stronger and more sensual version of Aqua Vitae, with added warmth and spice.

name: Aqua Celestia Cologne Forte
description: A luminous and fresh scent, evoking a clear blue sky, with lime and blackcurrant.

name: Aqua Celestia Forte
description: A more intense and bright version of Aqua Celestia, with rich floral and green notes.

name: Aqua Media Cologne Forte
description: A joyful and green fragrance, a bridge between sky and water, with bergamot and fennel.

name: Grand Soir
description: A warm, ambery fragrance that evokes the magic of a Parisian evening.

name: Petit Matin
description: A fresh and luminous fragrance, capturing the soft light of a Parisian morning.

name: A La Rose Eau de Parfum
description: A tribute to femininity, a declaration of love for all women captured in a fragrance, with two types of rose.
notes_middle: Bulgarian Rose, Grasses Rose, Violet, Magnolia

name: A La Rose L'Eau A La Rose
description: A lighter and fresher interpretation of A La Rose, sparkling with dewy rose petals and fruit.

name: L'Homme À la Rose
description: A fresh and modern rose fragrance for men, challenging traditional notions of masculinity.

name: Amyris Femme Eau de Parfum
description: A bright and vibrant floral-woody-amber fragrance, combining amyris and iris.

name: Amyris Femme Extrait de Parfum
description: A more intense and sensual version of Amyris Femme, amplifying its woody and amber facets.

name: Amyris Homme Eau de Toilette
description: A fresh and vibrant woody-aromatic fragrance for men, with amyris and rosemary.

name: Amyris Homme Extrait de Parfum
description: A more powerful and sophisticated version of Amyris Homme, intensifying its woody and amber character.

name: Gentle Fluidity Gold
description: Two eaux de parfum, two distinct olfactory silhouettes, using the same ingredients, highlighting a warm, generous trail.

name: Gentle Fluidity Silver
description: Two eaux de parfum, two distinct olfactory silhouettes, using the same ingredients, highlighting a fresh, vibrant trail.
A luminous, crisp, and energetic urban fragrance, inspired by the rhythm of New York City.

name: Absolue Pour le Matin
description: A bright and citrusy cologne, capturing the fresh light of dawn. (Discontinued)

name: Absolue Pour le Soir
description: A warm and sensual oriental fragrance, evoking the rich aromas of a summer evening. (Discontinued)

name: Féminin Pluriel
description: A beautiful bouquet of floral notes for a truly multifaceted woman.
notes_top: Iris, Violet, Rose, Jasmine, Lily-of-the-Valley, Orange Blossom

name: Masculin Pluriel
description: A timeless and elegant fougère for a man with multiple facets.

name: Relets d'Ambre
description: A very rare or possibly discontinued fragrance, likely featuring amber notes.
